  "source_text": {
    "text_id": "text_002",
    "title": "《地书》13点",
    "source": "教师提供",
    "raw_text": "我走在斑马线上，心里盘算着给她准备一份生日礼物——她马上就要30岁了。\n\n我又想到，要是送她一份求婚礼物，我们就能结婚了，可送什么好呢？\n\n她喜欢香奈儿，可我没钱，买不起。\n\n走着走着，我看到一家书店，想到书也是个不错的礼物。\n\n我走进书店，翻了翻书，突然想到可以在书里夹一朵玫瑰，可玫瑰很快就枯萎了，我的心也跟着碎了。我又想到书里藏着坏人，用枪指着我，有点害怕。\n\n坏人开枪打我，我躲开了，有点生气。我看着机票，想去旅行，忍不住笑了。\n\n我想到我们结婚后去度蜜月，笑了。我拿起手机给她发消息。\n\n我问她：\"结婚后想去哪度蜜月？\"她回：\"想去自由女神像，还有埃菲尔铁塔……\"\n\n电话响了，我看着机票，想去悉尼歌剧院、富士山、泰姬陵、加拿大、金字塔……最后选了美国。\n\n美国的景点有白宫、迪士尼、梦露、体育馆、自由女神像、世贸中心。\n\n我想到世贸中心被炸了，有点惊讶。\n\n我查了去美国的航班、机场、酒店和攻略。\n\n各种酒店都列了出来，五星的、三星的、经济型的，还有博物馆、剧院，各种奢侈品品牌。\n\n我点了赞，笑着继续翻书，走着走着到了门口，红灯亮了，停了下来。\n\n我想到她，转身往回走，又查了巴黎的景点，巴黎圣母院、蒙娜丽莎、埃菲尔铁塔……到了门口。\n\n我刷卡结账，想着买两本书当礼物。\n\n付了钱，拿到了礼物，想到她会很开心。\n\n我看着礼物，纠结要不要送她。\n\n走出书店，想到她的生日，又回头看了看。\n\n我想着相机太贵，不买；平板太贵，不买；滑板太贵，不买；游戏不贵，买了，忍不住笑了。\n\n我想到她和游戏，还是去结账吧。\n\n结完账，走出书店，看了看时间，回公司。\n\n刷了工牌，走进电梯，看到快递的牌子，有点惊讶。\n\n按了电梯，电梯到了1、2……89楼，红灯停了，开门，出去。\n\n左转，直行，转弯，直行，再转弯，直行，打卡，刷手机，开门。\n\n走到工位，坐下。",
    "notes": "标注说明"
  },
  "units": [
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_001",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我走在斑马线上，心里盘算着给她准备一份生日礼物——她马上就要30岁了。",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_002",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我又想到，要是送她一份求婚礼物，我们就能结婚了，可送什么好呢？",
      "sentence_index": 2,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_003",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "她喜欢香奈儿，可我没钱，买不起。",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_004",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走着走着，我看到一家书店，想到书也是个不错的礼物。",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_005",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我走进书店，翻了翻书，突然想到可以在书里夹一朵玫瑰，可玫瑰很快就枯萎了，我的心也跟着碎了。",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_006",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我又想到书里藏着坏人，用枪指着我，有点害怕。",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_007",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "坏人开枪打我，我躲开了，有点生气。",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_008",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着机票，想去旅行，忍不住笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_009",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到我们结婚后去度蜜月，笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_010",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我拿起手机给她发消息。",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_011",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我问她：\"结婚后想去哪度蜜月？\"她回：\"想去自由女神像，还有埃菲尔铁塔……\"",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_012",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "电话响了，我看着机票，想去悉尼歌剧院、富士山、泰姬陵、加拿大、金字塔……最后选了美国。",
      "sentence_index": 12,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_013",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "美国的景点有白宫、迪士尼、梦露、体育馆、自由女神像、世贸中心。",
      "sentence_index": 13,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_014",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到世贸中心被炸了，有点惊讶。",
      "sentence_index": 14,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_015",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我查了去美国的航班、机场、酒店和攻略。",
      "sentence_index": 15,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_016",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "各种酒店都列了出来，五星的、三星的、经济型的，还有博物馆、剧院，各种奢侈品品牌。",
      "sentence_index": 16,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_017",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我点了赞，笑着继续翻书，走着走着到了门口，红灯亮了，停了下来。",
      "sentence_index": 17,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_018",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到她，转身往回走，又查了巴黎的景点，巴黎圣母院、蒙娜丽莎、埃菲尔铁塔……到了门口。",
      "sentence_index": 18,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_019",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我刷卡结账，想着买两本书当礼物。",
      "sentence_index": 19,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_020",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "付了钱，拿到了礼物，想到她会很开心。",
      "sentence_index": 20,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_021",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着礼物，纠结要不要送她。",
      "sentence_index": 21,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_022",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走出书店，想到她的生日，又回头看了看。",
      "sentence_index": 22,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_023",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想着相机太贵，不买；平板太贵，不买；滑板太贵，不买；游戏不贵，买了，忍不住笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 23,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_024",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到她和游戏，还是去结账吧。",
      "sentence_index": 24,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_025",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "结完账，走出书店，看了看时间，回公司。",
      "sentence_index": 25,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_026",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "刷了工牌，走进电梯，看到快递的牌子，有点惊讶。",
      "sentence_index": 26,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_027",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "按了电梯，电梯到了1、2……89楼，红灯停了，开门，出去。",
      "sentence_index": 27,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_028",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "左转，直行，转弯，直行，再转弯，直行，打卡，刷手机，开门。",
      "sentence_index": 28,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_029",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走到工位，坐下。",
      "sentence_index": 29,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 0,
      "children": []
    }
  ],
